Unordered Lists

     * This is a list item in an unordered list
     * An unordered list is a list in which the sequence of items is not
       important. Sometimes, an unordered list is a bulleted list. And
       this is a long list item in an unordered list that can wrap onto a
       new line.
     * Lists can be nested inside of each other
          + This is a nested list item
               o This is a nested list item
               o This is another nested list item in an unordered list
          + This is another nested list item in an unordered list
     * This is the last list item

Ordered Lists

    1. This is a list item in an ordered list
    2. An ordered list is a list in which the sequence of items is
       important. An ordered list does not necessarily contain sequence
       characters.
    3. Lists can be nested inside of each other
         1. This is a nested list item
              1. This is a nested list item
              2. This is another nested list item in an ordered list
         2. This is another nested list item in an ordered list
    4. This is the last list item
